  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The generation of a good surgical field at the mid-lower mediastinum during thoracoscopic&#xD;
      esophagectomy in the left lateral decubitus position is often complicated. The investigators&#xD;
      developed a simple and useful technique for surgical field generation.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
